                "invention-title": [
                    "Comprehensive energy utilization system and method for residential houses",
                    "民用住宅综合能源利用系统及方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention provides a residential building comprehensive energy utilization system and method, and the system comprises a water electrolysis hydrogen production device which is electrically connected with a bus through a second line; a switch II is arranged on the circuit II; a gas outlet I of the water electrolysis hydrogen production device is connected with a gas inlet of the hydrogen fuel battery pack; the hydrogen fuel battery pack is connected with the bus through a line I; a switch I is arranged on the circuit I; the hydrogen storage tank is connected with a gas outlet II of the water electrolysis hydrogen production device through a pipeline I, and is connected with a gas inlet of the hydrogen fuel battery pack through a pipeline II; a valve I is arranged on the pipeline I; a valve II is arranged on the pipeline II; the hydrogen energy combustion device is connected with a gas outlet III of the water electrolysis hydrogen production device through a pipeline III; a valve III is arranged on the pipeline III; the commercial power access device is connected with the bus through a third line, and the third line is provided with a third switch. And a power manager. The access sequence of the normal electric energy unit, the hydrogen fuel battery pack and the mains supply can be adjusted in real time according to the power utilization condition, and energy waste is reduced on the premise that the energy utilization requirement of residents is met."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明提出了一种民用住宅综合能源利用系统及方法，该系统包括：电解水制氢装置，通过线路二与母线电连接；线路二上设置开关二；电解水制氢装置的出气口一连接氢燃料电池组的进气口；氢燃料电池组，通过线路一连接母线；线路一上设置开关一；储氢罐，通过管路一连接电解水制氢装置的出气口二，储氢罐通过管路二连接氢燃料电池组的进气口；管路一上设置阀一，管路二上设置阀二；氢能燃烧装置，通过管路三连接电解水制氢装置的出气口三；管路三上设置阀三；市电接入装置通过线路三连接母线、线路三上设置开关三；及电能管理器。本发明可根据用电情况实时调节常态电能单元，氢燃料电池组及市电的接入顺序，在满足居民用能需求的前提下，减少能源浪费。"
                }
            ]
